Zvec  (Foundation.AI.VectorStore.Zvec, Zvec, Zvec.Engine, Zvec.Bench, Zvec.Test)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Zvec family of projects is a .NET port of "zvec" by Alibaba Group:

    https://github.com/alibaba/zvec

The original C++ implementation is licensed under the Apache License 2.0
(included as LICENSE in this distribution and applicable to the upstream work).
The .NET port preserves the in-process embedded-vector-database architecture
(dense + sparse vectors, hybrid search with structured filters, concurrent
reads with exclusive writes, write-ahead logging) and reimplements the core
similarity-search routines in C# with platform-specific SIMD where available.

Copyright (c) Alibaba Group Holding Limited and contributors.

