Foundation.AI.MarkItDown
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Foundation.AI.MarkItDown family is conceptually inspired by Microsoft's
Python "markitdown" library:

    https://github.com/microsoft/markitdown

It is an independent .NET implementation, not a direct port of the Python code.
No Microsoft source code is included or redistributed.

